## Project Overview

**Name:** Universal AI Student Gateway (Student Portal Gateway)  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Type:** Secure automation and AI layer for college portals  
**License:** MIT  

A secure automation and AI layer that sits between students and their college portals, enabling monitoring, notifications, and automated portal management. This is a linking interface for students to connect and manage their college portals.

---

## What This Does

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Monitor** | Automatically monitors your college portal |
| **Notify** | Alerts when important updates occur (results, notices, fees) |
| **Control** | Control your portal through the app (apply for exams, pay fees, etc.) |
| **AI Insights** | AI-powered insights about your academic progress |
| **Multi-Channel Notifications** | Push, WhatsApp, SMS, Email |

---

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Frontend (Next.js 14)                     │
│  - Dashboard, Portal Management, Real-time Updates           │
└──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                       │ HTTPS/REST API
                       │
┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  API Gateway (NestJS)                        │
│  - JWT Auth, Request Validation, Rate Limiting, CORS         │
└──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                       │
        ┌──────────────┼──────────────┐
        │              │              │
┌───────▼──────┐ ┌─────▼──────┐ ┌────▼─────────┐
│ Auth Service │ │ Portals   │ │ AI Service   │
└──────────────┘ └─────┬──────┘ └──────────────┘
                       │
┌───────▼──────┐ ┌─────▼──────┐ ┌────▼─────────┐
│ Vault        │ │ Automation │ │ Notifications│
│ Service      │ │ Service    │ │ Service      │
└──────┬───────┘ └─────┬──────┘ └──────────────┘
       │                │
       ▼                ▼
Encrypted Vault    Playwright (Headless Browser)
       │                │
       └────────────────▼────────────────────
                  College Portals (ERP, LMS, Exam)
```

**Data Flow:**
- **Portal Connection:** User credentials → AES-256-GCM encrypt → Vault → Token in DB
- **Portal Sync:** Scheduler → Decrypt → Playwright login → Scrape data → Compare state → Notify if changed
- **Action Execution:** User request → AI analysis → Vault → Browser automation → Screenshot → Result

