## Database Schema

### Users
| Column | Type |
|--------|------|
| id | uuid (PK) |
| email | string (unique) |
| passwordHash | string |
| firstName | string |
| lastName | string |
| phoneNumber | string (nullable) |
| isActive | boolean |
| createdAt | timestamp |
| updatedAt | timestamp |

### Portal Connections
| Column | Type |
|--------|------|
| id | uuid (PK) |
| user_id | uuid (FK) |
| portalType | enum (amity, upes, du, vit, iit, custom) |
| portalUrl | string |
| collegeId | string |
| credential_token | string |
| isActive | boolean |
| autoSync | boolean |
| syncIntervalMinutes | int (default 15) |
| createdAt | timestamp |
| updatedAt | timestamp |

### Portal States, Portal Audit Logs
See `backend/src/portals/entities/` for full definitions.

