## API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/auth/register` | Register (email, password, firstName, lastName) |
| POST | `/auth/login` | Login |
| GET | `/auth/me` | Get profile (JWT required) |

### Portals (all require JWT)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/portals/connect` | Create connection |
| GET | `/portals` | List user connections |
| GET | `/portals/summary` | Dashboard summary |
| GET | `/portals/:id` | Get connection |
| POST | `/portals/:id/sync` | Trigger sync |
| GET | `/portals/:id/state` | Latest state |
| GET | `/portals/:id/insights` | AI insights |
| POST | `/portals/:id/action` | Perform action |
| DELETE | `/portals/:id` | Soft delete (set isActive=false) |
| GET | `/portals/:id/assignments` | List assignments |
| GET | `/portals/:id/assignments/:assignmentId` | Get assignment |
| POST | `/portals/:id/assignments/:assignmentId/review` | Review assignment (file upload) |
| POST | `/portals/:id/assignments/:assignmentId/submit` | Submit assignment (file upload) |
| GET | `/portals/:id/audit-logs` | Audit logs |

